<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA525_02_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema525_02_ih_0002.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema525_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema525_02_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">직육면체에 대한 설명입니다. 알맞은 말에 ○표 하세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box dir_col gap_40">
          <div class="text_bullet" lang="y">
            선분으로 둘러싸인 부분을 (
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="true"><span>면</span></button>, <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>모서리</span></button>,
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>꼭짓점</span></button>
            </div>
            )(이)라고 합니다.
          </div>
          <div class="text_bullet" lang="y">
            면과 면이 만나는 선분을 (
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>면</span></button>, <button type="button" data-answer-single="true"><span>모서리</span></button>,
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>꼭짓점</span></button>
            </div>
            )(이)라고 합니다.
          </div>
          <div class="text_bullet" lang="y">
            모서리와 모서리가 만나는 점을 (
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>면</span></button>, <button type="button" data-answer-single="false"><span>모서리</span></button>,
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="true"><span>꼭짓점</span></button>
            </div>
            )(이)라고 합니다.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">면: 선분으로 둘러싸인 부분</p>
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">모서리: 면과 면이 만나는 선분</p>
                <p class="text_bullet" lang="y">꼭짓점: 모서리와 모서리가 만나는 점</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
